The '''Lodon Ocean''' was one of three major [[Ocean/Legends|oceans]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Elrood/Legends|Elrood]]. It was the northernmost ocean and was located on the edge of Elrood's largest continent. The city of [[Dinbar/Legends|Dinbar]] was located on the western bank of this body of water.

